Lyndsey Marshal https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lyndsey_Marshal 0 Lyndsey Marshal (born 16 June 1978) is an English actress best known for her performance in The Hours, and as the recurring character Cleopatra on HBO's Rome, and as Lady Sarah Hill in BBC period drama Garrow's Law.
